data.description: Brick home, new water heater in 2022, new microwave, bedroom and bathroom flooring  in 2023. Owners love the great outdoors and have removed dead trees, reconfigured the driveway, restored lawn, installed raised beds, planted 12 assorted types of trees, perennials, and herbs. Enjoy quiet evenings at the gazebo, while cooking dinner at the firepit , complete with grill assembly during the warmer months. Stay cozy indoors at the fireplace, or enjoy the view from the family room during the colder months thanks to the sunroom feeling  with a wall of windows in the family room.  30x40 pole​​‌​​​​‌​‌​​​‌​​​​‌‌​​​​​​‌‌​​​​ barn
